22a_marginbottom5 indo-1d70522a_marginleft0 indo-1d70522a_marginright0 indo-26838ee5_paddingleft0 indo-26838ee5_paddingright0 indo-7199e23_root indo-804a7bc3_root" data-auth-intro="article" data-testid="article-intro"><p>据目击者称，周末，史蒂夫·布西密在一家爱尔兰酒吧外帮助制止了一场“恶性斗殴”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/wednesday-review-netflix-addams-family-3353922"><b>《星期三》评论：Netflix 的《亚当斯一家》衍生剧令人毛骨悚然、怪异且非常诡异</b></a></li></ul></div><div class="indo-1d70522a_marginleft0 indo-1d70522a_marginright0 indo-26838ee5_paddingleft0 indo-26838ee5_paddingright0 indo-804a7bc3_root" data-testid="article-body"><p>周六晚上（8 月 31 日） <em>，这位大勒博斯基</em>演员被发现在都柏林南部小镇达尔基的布巴鱼市场吃饭。</p><p>布西密目前正在拍摄<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>热门剧集<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/wednesday"><em>周三</em></a>的新一季，该剧集由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jenna-ortega">珍娜·奥尔特加 (Jenna Ortega)</a>主演，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tim-burton">蒂姆·波顿 (Tim Burton)</a>执导。</p><p> “除了我之外，我这一桌没有人认出他；我是一个超级电影迷，所以我立刻就认识了他，”用餐者奥伊辛·希维 (Oisín Heavey) 告诉《 <a href="https://www.independent.ie/style/celebrity/celebrity-news/actor-steve-buscemi-intervenes-after-fight-outside-dalkey-pub/a1514809758.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>爱尔兰独立报》</em></a> 。我们正在吃晚饭，他在我们旁边的桌子上待了 90 分钟。”</p><p>演员吃完饭后，希维说，他的妻子注意到餐厅外聚集了一群人，他们认为这是为了演员。 </p></div><div data-testid="article-body"></div><div class="indo-1d70522a_marginleft0 indo-1d70522a_marginright0 indo-26838ee5_paddingleft0 indo-26838ee5_paddingright0 indo-804a7bc3_root" data-testid="article-body"><figure id="attachment_3755569" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3755569" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3755569" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/steve-buscemi@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/steve-buscemi@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.