an-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/fatman-scoop-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/missy-elliott">Missy Elliott</a> 、 <a href="/artists/ciara">Ciara</a> 、 <a href="/artists/questlove">Questlove</a> 、 <a href="/artists/nicki-minaj">Nicki Minaj</a>等人向已故的<a href="/artists/fatman-scoop">Fatman Scoop</a>致敬。</p><p>这位传奇说唱歌手、炒作者、DJ 和制作人的真名艾萨克·弗里曼三世 (Isaac Freeman III) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rap-icon-fatman-scoop-has-died-after-suffering-medical-emergency-on-stage-3789417">于周六（8 月 31 日）去世，</a>享年 52 岁。Scoop 前一天晚上在康涅狄格州的一场演出中在舞台上晕倒，被紧急送往医院。他的死因仍不清楚。自消息传出以来，音乐界的多位合作者和其他重要人物都向 Scoop 表示敬意。</p><p> <a href="/artists/timbaland">Timbaland</a>在获得格莱美奖和 MTV VMA 奖项后发布了一张 Freeman 的照片，称他“不知所措”，他们 2001 年合作的《Drop》——最近因 TikTok 重新流行起来——是他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/missy-elliott-out-of-this-world-debut-north-america-tour-tickets-3614871">《Drop》节目</a>中的开场曲。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/missy-elliott-out-of-this-world-debut-north-america-tour-tickets-3614871">走出这个世界的巡演</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_VtE-xR7qH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;">